(239, 1, '2012-07-30 03:02:19', '2012-07-30 03:02:19', '<strong><a href="http://sevima.com/sevima_new/">SEVIMA.COM </a></strong>- CSS background properties biasanya digunakan untuk memberi warna/ gambar pada latar belakang pada suatu elemen.\r\n\r\nContoh :\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;html&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;head&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;style type="text/css"&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">body {</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">background-color:#b0c4de;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">h1 {</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">background-color:#6495ed;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">p {</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">background-color:#e0ffff;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">div {</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">background-color:#b0c4de;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;/style&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;/head&gt; </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;body&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;h1&gt;CSS background-color example!&lt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;div&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">This is a text inside a div element.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;p&gt;This paragraph has it''s own backg</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">We are still in the div element.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;/div&gt; </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;/body&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">&lt;/html&gt;</span>\r\n\r\nHasilnya :\r\n\r\n<img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Cara Menggunakan CSS Backgrounds', '', 'publish', 'op